name: Shanzhagao 山楂糕 / Some sort of style Lora
description:
为什么叫山楂糕呢？因为它软软甜甜、酸爽不腻~

Eng description below. 更多例图下面相册请~

Feel free to merge this lora into lora/models/anything else that I don't know (if only you aren't trying to make money from it of course). 如想与其他lora/模型等混合，只要不盈利——敬请随意。

为什么上面例图显示inpaint：我用了Tiled Diffusion, 也就是 Multidiffusion 插件来upscale，主要就是会让图片更好看，你可以用常规方式upscale，当然也可以用txt2img产图。

https://civitai.com/posts/136081 MD前原图在这儿~

Reason why the sample images displayed as inpainting: I'm using the Tiled Diffusion, aka Multidiffusion plugin to upscale, you can of course generate with txt2img——myself did that, and sent the outcome to img2img, then upscaled it lel. https://civitai.com/posts/136081 Original files generated using txt2img here.

这个风格lora里有一个软软的画风，触发token我设置成了child，会让眼睛圆圆的，腮帮肉肉的，总之可爱的（

其余推荐使用token: hanfu, red lips, scenery, east asian architecture, light rays, light particles, sparkle, sliding doors, glowing

推荐CFG：如果没有Dynamic Thresholding就7，但是我强烈推荐Dynamic Thresholding插件，开20CFG，所有东西都好看一万倍（？

推荐分辨率：啥·都·行·呀，图里你们也看见了啥分辨率都有，就没不行的（草

推荐模型：我是在based64mix上测试的，风格最贴近原版，不过AOM3也不是不行，其他的自己试试也好啦。

I've set the trigger token of the "softer" style in this lora as child, makes the eyes larger, cheeks pinchier, everything cuter!

Recommended tokens: hanfu, red lips, scenery, east asian architecture, light rays, light particles, sparkle, sliding doors, glowing

Recommended CFG: 7 without Dynamic Thresholding Plugin, 14-20 with Dynamic Thresholding.

Recommended resolution: literally anything has been successful on my end, you can see it in the preview pics lel.

Recommended model: I've tested on based64mix, and the outcome is by far the best, however, AOM3、holokukiv2.2、somethingv2_2 could also produce some nice things, feel free to test on other models!
